{"tid":1404603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期抗爭] 請中產或以上搵你嘅另一半，生最少兩個小朋友","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T06:31:57.000Z","uid":48234,"like":77,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"56bc3149988bc7fec8e7baaed4f83215f59c8712","tid":1404603,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">前提: 拒絕蚑那蝗另一半!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人有責任同返香港人生兒育女<br />\n生兩個或以上，增加正宗香港人人口<br />\n從小訓練小朋友體能，獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n我知道有人打算變性<br />\n你哋可以諗一諗:<br />\n可唔可以生完兩三個，完成抗爭任務之後先變性?<br />\n<br />\n窮人生仔係正仆街，但係而家香港要人!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔生仔/女係損害香港!<br />\n仲仆街過窮人生仔!</span></span>"},{"pid":"1efff4b8df52023b4ac7f2334f1517cd55681ba5","tid":1404603,"uid":283157,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b68e9be06ee099cb212c9983aadb94e79a31015","tid":1404603,"uid":87890,"like":12,"dislike":24,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8350a5fe20b63ab70683b7ad0d5d023a440da6d9","tid":1404603,"uid":48234,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e980fd0fab6f3098103b5c9d8fcc32ee83c673","tid":1404603,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:29:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果香港輸就真係乜都冇晒!<br />\n請大家幫幫手!<br />\n冇香港人又點會有香港?<br />\n我唔想香港滅亡!</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf563e91bf97670e758e7680ac9cc0318199a272","tid":1404603,"uid":164920,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"抗共還抗共，仔女唔係你既工具"},{"pid":"3b32c463bc7c6022f6c694e573